fields.name: Effect:
fields.value: Attack another player for 2 HP of damage. Apply 1 phase of Weakened if not defended.

fields.name: Upgraded:
fields.value:
Attack another player for 5 HP of damage. Apply 1 phase of Weakened, and 2 more if not defended.

*Status takes effect next phase. Read <#1191650444594909354> for more information on player statuses.*
